title: Every single way you can pre-order the Apple iPhone 6s, iPhone 6s Plus in India ahead of October 16 launch
text: Apple’s new iPhone 6s and iPhone 6s Plus are set to go on sale in India on October 16. With less than a week to go, e-commerce sites and offline retailers have started taking pre-orders for Apple’s new iPhones. If you are planning on buying either of the new iPhones, but are overwhelmed with the myriad of options, we have made things easier for you by collating all options in one place. Let’s start with the pricing first. While Apple hasn’t made an official announcement, the e-commerce sites have revealed the official prices, and they are in line with earlier reports. Prices for the iPhone 6s start from Rs 62,000 for the 16GB variant, Rs 72,000 for the 64GB variant »
